flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE is a free Linux-based operating system for your PC, Laptop or Server. You can surf the web, manage your e-mails and photos, do office work, play videos or music
This DVD includes everything to make your desktop, notebook or server up and running in no time!
— Processor: Intel: Pentium 1-4, Xeon or newer; AMD: Duron, Athlon, Athlon XP,MP,64, Sempron, Opteron or newer.
— Hard Disk: At least 500MB for minimal system; 2.5GB recommended for standard system.
— Graphics and Sound Card: Supports most modern sound and graphics cards.
Be part of the openSUSE community!
F-Spot photo management and editing application as included in openSUSE 11.2
